title: Sky Taxi v1.0-TE
description:
Release: 2009
Genre: Arcade
Developer: Sky Bros
Language: En

Mitch and has pals just want to sit around and watch TV. But the Fairy Queen has an important assignment for them: rescue her people from nasty aliens!


Run, jump and stomp your way to fortune and fame as you collect goodies and knock the living stars out of your enemies. You can also launch off clouds and leap through fire to discover amazing secrets and play mini-games to enhance your skills. Can you prove yourself worthy of a Kung Fu upgrade? Sky Taxi offers a fun challenge for everyone in your family!

Key Game Features

* More than 180 levels
* 10 super bosses
* 25 rare secret items
* Arcade mini-games
* Simple gameplay
